title: Bug 121682: Exception thrown when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description: Description: An exception is thrown when exporting data from the attached report.
OB: When exporting data from a table containing highlight/map, an exception is thrown in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() method.
EB: When exporting the data from a table, the data should be successfully exported without any exceptions.
SR:
To reproduce the issue, follow these steps:
1. Open the attached report.
2. Export the data from a table containing highlight/map.
3. Observe the exception thrown in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() method.
